The paper deals with cybersecurity and the analysis of data sets related to cyberattacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves network analysis and prediction, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The use of quantitative measures and machine learning techniques indicates that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
